/****************************************************
 * sparcal - a pascal to SPARC (also ARM!) compiler *
 ****************************************************/

To build and run a quick example compilation, run the following from here:

	pushd src && make clean && make && make demo && popd

To just build the compiler:

	pushd src && make clean && make && popd

To run the interpereter:

	sparcal -l pascal_program.p

To run the emitter (output SPARC assembly to stdout):

	sparcal -e pascal_program.p

To run the emitter (output ARM assembly to stdout):

	sparcal -ea pascal_program.p
